#: ../../source/screens.rst:1788
msgid ""
"An imagemap creates a fixed, allowing any child to be added to it (not just "
"hotspots and hotbars)."
msgstr ""
"imagemap は fixed を作成し、 ( hotspot と hotbar だけでなく ) すべての子をそ"
